# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Root .env example.
#
# The backend reads its configuration from backend/.env (see backend/.env.example).
# This root file documents the same variables for convenience and CI usage.
# Copy backend/.env.example -> backend/.env and fill in real values before
# running `docker compose up`.
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------

# See backend/.env.example for the full, authoritative variable list:
#   - Azure AI Search : AZURE_SEARCH_*
#   - Azure Cosmos DB : COSMOS_*
#   - Azure Redis     : REDIS_*
#   - Google Gemini   : GOOGLE_API_KEY, GEMINI_*, EMBEDDING_DIMENSIONS
